Features of our software: 
1. If you are a voter then only you have chance to vote. 
2. Repeated voters are not allowed to vote. 
3. We can set the time period for polling. 
4. After dead line, if voter tries to vote the result will be displayed to the election officer. 
5. If there is draw between any of the contestants, it displays draw between them. 
6. we can either register for voting or we can pledge our vote. 
